## Q67

Question:
Lateral wall of Nasopharynx contain all except

Option A:
Torus tubarius

Option B:
Fossa of Rosemuller

Option C:
Basilar portion of sphenoid

Option D:
Pharyngo tympanic tube

Correct Answer:
